    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="传热学笔记"><a href="#传热学笔记" class="headerlink" title=" 传热学笔记"></a><center> 传热学笔记</center></h1><h1 id="第一章-绪论"><a href="#第一章-绪论" class="headerlink" title="第一章 绪论"></a>第一章 绪论</h1><h2 id="1-2-热量传递的基本方式"><a href="#1-2-热量传递的基本方式" class="headerlink" title="1.2 热量传递的基本方式"></a>1.2 热量传递的基本方式</h2><h4 id="传热的三种方式："><a href="#传热的三种方式：" class="headerlink" title="==传热的三种方式：=="></a>==<strong>传热的三种方式：</strong>==</h4><p>热传导、热对流、热辐射</p><h3 id="1-2-1-热传导"><a href="#1-2-1-热传导" class="headerlink" title="1.2.1 热传导"></a>1.2.1 热传导</h3><h4 id="一维热传导方程："><a href="#一维热传导方程：" class="headerlink" title="==一维热传导方程：=="></a><u>==<strong>一维热传导方程：</strong>==</u></h4><p>$$<br>\phi =A\lambda \frac{t_{w1} -t_{w2}}{\delta }<br>$$</p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209051909921.png"></p><h2 id="例题"><a href="#例题" class="headerlink" title="例题"></a>例题</h2><p><strong>例1.1：</strong></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209051909125.png"><br>$$<br>q=796000 (W/m^{2} )<br>$$</p><h2 id="1-3-传热过程和导热系数"><a href="#1-3-传热过程和导热系数" class="headerlink" title="1.3 传热过程和导热系数"></a>1.3 传热过程和导热系数</h2><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209051909019.png"></p><h3 id="传热过程热流量公式"><a href="#传热过程热流量公式" class="headerlink" title="==传热过程热流量公式=="></a>==<u>传热过程热流量公式</u>==</h3><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209051910712.png"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209051910079.png"></p><h2 id="例题-1"><a href="#例题-1" class="headerlink" title="例题"></a>例题</h2><p><strong>例1.2：</strong></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209051911053.png"></p><p><strong>例1.3：</strong></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209051912288.png"></p><h1 id="第二章-导热基本定律"><a href="#第二章-导热基本定律" class="headerlink" title="第二章 导热基本定律"></a>第二章 导热基本定律</h1><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209051913514.png"></p><h2 id="2-1-导热基本定律–傅里叶定律"><a href="#2-1-导热基本定律–傅里叶定律" class="headerlink" title="2.1 导热基本定律–傅里叶定律"></a>2.1 导热基本定律–傅里叶定律</h2><h3 id="2-1-1-温度场"><a href="#2-1-1-温度场" class="headerlink" title="2.1.1 温度场"></a>2.1.1 温度场</h3><p>一维稳态温度场：$ t=f(x) $</p><p>等温面、等温线</p><h3 id="2-1-2-导热基本定律"><a href="#2-1-2-导热基本定律" class="headerlink" title="2.1.2 导热基本定律"></a>2.1.2 导热基本定律</h3><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209051913541.png"></p><h3 id="2-1-3-导热系数"><a href="#2-1-3-导热系数" class="headerlink" title="2.1.3 导热系数"></a>2.1.3 导热系数</h3><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209051915411.png"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209051915099.png" alt="QQ截图20220905173503"></p><h2 id="例题-2"><a href="#例题-2" class="headerlink" title="例题"></a>例题</h2><p><strong>例2.1</strong></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209051915231.png" alt="QQ截图20220905173944"></p><h2 id="2-2-傅里叶定律"><a href="#2-2-傅里叶定律" class="headerlink" title="2.2 傅里叶定律"></a>2.2 傅里叶定律</h2><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209051914591.png"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209051914613.png"></p><h2 id="2-3-导热率"><a href="#2-3-导热率" class="headerlink" title="2.3 导热率"></a>2.3 导热率</h2><h3 id="湿度"><a href="#湿度" class="headerlink" title="湿度"></a>湿度</h3><p>绝热保温材料受湿度影响较大，同时也要考虑防冻。</p><h2 id="2-4-导热问题的数学描述"><a href="#2-4-导热问题的数学描述" class="headerlink" title="2.4 导热问题的数学描述"></a>2.4 导热问题的数学描述</h2><h3 id="2-4-1-导热微分方程"><a href="#2-4-1-导热微分方程" class="headerlink" title="2.4.1 导热微分方程"></a>2.4.1 导热微分方程</h3><p><strong>理论基础：</strong>傅里叶定律+能量守恒定律</p><p><strong>对导热物体作几点假设：</strong></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071807300.png" alt="QQ截图20220907161745"></p><p><strong>数学模型的建立：</strong></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071810901.png" alt="QQ截图20220907162415"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071810277.png" alt="QQ截图20220907163412"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071811448.png" alt="QQ截图20220907163649"></p><p><strong>推导得：</strong></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071811972.png" alt="QQ截图20220907163900"></p><h4 id="化简得："><a href="#化简得：" class="headerlink" title="==化简得：=="></a><u>==化简得：==</u></h4><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071811343.png" alt="QQ截图20220907164038"></p><p><strong>热扩散率：</strong></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071811510.png" alt="QQ截图20220907165721"></p><p><strong>引入拉普拉斯算子化简得：</strong></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071811849.png" alt="QQ截图20220907170156"></p><h4 id="不同情况下的微分方程："><a href="#不同情况下的微分方程：" class="headerlink" title="==不同情况下的微分方程：=="></a><u>==不同情况下的微分方程：==</u></h4><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071811563.png" alt="QQ截图20220907170146"></p><h4 id="热扩散率："><a href="#热扩散率：" class="headerlink" title="热扩散率："></a><strong>热扩散率：</strong></h4><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071811661.png" alt="QQ截图20220907171006"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071811166.png" alt="QQ截图20220907171226"></p><p><strong>总结：</strong></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071811674.png" alt="QQ截图20220907171340"></p><h3 id="2-4-2-定解条件"><a href="#2-4-2-定解条件" class="headerlink" title="2.4.2 定解条件"></a>2.4.2 定解条件</h3><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071811599.png" alt="QQ截图20220907171630"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071811860.png" alt="QQ截图20220907171830"></p><h4 id="初始条件（时间条件）："><a href="#初始条件（时间条件）：" class="headerlink" title="初始条件（时间条件）："></a>初始条件（时间条件）：</h4><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071811337.png" alt="QQ截图20220907172008"></p><h4 id="边界条件："><a href="#边界条件：" class="headerlink" title="==边界条件：=="></a>==边界条件：==</h4><ol><li>==第一类边界条件：已知任何时刻下，物体边界上的温度值…==</li></ol><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071811539.png" alt="QQ截图20220907172212"></p><ol start="2"><li>==第二类边界条件：已知物体边界上任何时刻热流密度的分布及变化规律、特例（绝热边界面）==</li></ol><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071811652.png" alt="QQ截图20220907172716"></p><ol start="3"><li>==第三类边界条件：已知任一时刻边界面的对流换热系数$$h$$和周围流体的温度$$t_{f} $$==</li></ol><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071812864.png" alt="QQ截图20220907173103"></p><h2 id="例题-3"><a href="#例题-3" class="headerlink" title="例题"></a>例题</h2><p><strong>例2.2</strong></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071812112.png" alt="QQ截图20220907173456"></p><p><strong>例2.3：</strong></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071812245.png" alt="QQ截图20220907173702"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209071812062.png" alt="QQ截图20220907173823"></p><p><strong>例2.3：</strong></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142044181.png" alt="QQ截图20220914160814"></p><p>4、一厚度为$$40mm$$的无限大平壁，其稳态温度分布为：$$ t=(180-1800x^{2})℃$$。若平壁材料导热系数$$=50W/(m.k)$$，试求:1.平壁两侧表面处的热流密度;2.平壁中是否有内热源?若有的话，它的强度是多大?</p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142044618.png" alt="QQ截图20220914160839"></p><h1 id="第三章-稳态导热"><a href="#第三章-稳态导热" class="headerlink" title="第三章 稳态导热"></a>第三章 稳态导热</h1><h2 id="3-1-通过平壁导热"><a href="#3-1-通过平壁导热" class="headerlink" title="3.1 通过平壁导热"></a>3.1 通过平壁导热</h2><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142044221.png" alt="QQ截图20220914161214"></p><h3 id="3-1-1-第一类边界条件下平壁一维稳态导热"><a href="#3-1-1-第一类边界条件下平壁一维稳态导热" class="headerlink" title="3.1.1 第一类边界条件下平壁一维稳态导热"></a>3.1.1 第一类边界条件下平壁一维稳态导热</h3><h4 id="1-单层平壁"><a href="#1-单层平壁" class="headerlink" title="1.单层平壁"></a>1.单层平壁</h4><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142044459.png" alt="QQ截图20220914162356"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142044355.png" alt="QQ截图20220914161905"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142044105.png" alt="QQ截图20220914162535"></p><h4 id="2-多层平壁"><a href="#2-多层平壁" class="headerlink" title="2.多层平壁"></a>2.多层平壁</h4><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142044097.png" alt="QQ截图20220914162918"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142044342.png" alt="QQ截图20220914163413"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142044242.png" alt="QQ截图20220914163518"></p><h3 id="例题："><a href="#例题：" class="headerlink" title="例题："></a><strong>例题：</strong></h3><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142044557.png" alt="QQ截图20220914164350"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142044374.png" alt="QQ截图20220914165938"></p><h3 id="3-1-2-第三类边界条件下平板一维稳态导热"><a href="#3-1-2-第三类边界条件下平板一维稳态导热" class="headerlink" title="3.1.2 第三类边界条件下平板一维稳态导热"></a>3.1.2 第三类边界条件下平板一维稳态导热</h3><h4 id="1-单层平壁-1"><a href="#1-单层平壁-1" class="headerlink" title="1.单层平壁"></a>1.单层平壁</h4><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142045217.png" alt="QQ截图20220914170506"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142045896.png" alt="QQ截图20220914170912"></p><h4 id="2-多层平壁-1"><a href="#2-多层平壁-1" class="headerlink" title="2.多层平壁"></a>2.多层平壁</h4><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142045782.png" alt="QQ截图20220914171031"></p><h3 id="例题：-1"><a href="#例题：-1" class="headerlink" title="例题："></a>例题：</h3><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142045343.png" alt="QQ截图20220914171221"></p><h2 id="3-2-通过圆筒壁的导热"><a href="#3-2-通过圆筒壁的导热" class="headerlink" title="3.2 通过圆筒壁的导热"></a>3.2 通过圆筒壁的导热</h2><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142045137.png" alt="QQ截图20220914172730"></p><h3 id="3-2-1第一类边界条件下单层圆筒壁稳态导热量"><a href="#3-2-1第一类边界条件下单层圆筒壁稳态导热量" class="headerlink" title="3.2.1第一类边界条件下单层圆筒壁稳态导热量"></a>3.2.1第一类边界条件下单层圆筒壁稳态导热量</h3><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142045833.png" alt="QQ截图20220914172942"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142045364.png" alt="QQ截图20220914173252"></p><h3 id="3-2-2第三类边界条件下单层圆筒壁稳态导热量"><a href="#3-2-2第三类边界条件下单层圆筒壁稳态导热量" class="headerlink" title="3.2.2第三类边界条件下单层圆筒壁稳态导热量"></a>3.2.2第三类边界条件下单层圆筒壁稳态导热量</h3><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209142045454.png" alt="QQ截图20220914173607"></p><h3 id="3-2-3第一、三类边界条件下n层圆筒壁稳态导热量"><a href="#3-2-3第一、三类边界条件下n层圆筒壁稳态导热量" class="headerlink" title="3.2.3第一、三类边界条件下n层圆筒壁稳态导热量"></a>3.2.3第一、三类边界条件下n层圆筒壁稳态导热量</h3><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209191616745.png" alt="QQ截图20220919161510"></p><h2 id="例题-4"><a href="#例题-4" class="headerlink" title="例题"></a>例题</h2><p>例3.1</p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209211739639.png" alt="QQ截图20220921171752"></p><p>例3.2</p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209211739962.png" alt="QQ截图20220921173124"></p><p>例3.3</p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209211741784.png" alt="QQ截图20220921173733"></p><h1 id="第四章-非稳态导热"><a href="#第四章-非稳态导热" class="headerlink" title="第四章 非稳态导热"></a>第四章 非稳态导热</h1><h2 id="4-1-基本概念"><a href="#4-1-基本概念" class="headerlink" title="4.1 基本概念"></a>4.1 基本概念</h2><h3 id="4-1-1-定义及分类"><a href="#4-1-1-定义及分类" class="headerlink" title="4.1.1 定义及分类"></a>4.1.1 定义及分类</h3><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209191621986.png" alt="QQ截图20220919162036"></p><h3 id="4-1-2-不同阶段"><a href="#4-1-2-不同阶段" class="headerlink" title="4.1.2 不同阶段"></a>4.1.2 不同阶段</h3><p>瞬态导热有三个阶段：初始阶段、发展阶段、稳定阶段</p><h3 id="4-1-3"><a href="#4-1-3" class="headerlink" title="4.1.3"></a>4.1.3</h3><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209191721926.png" alt="QQ截图20220919162921"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209191721250.png" alt="QQ截图20220919163356"></p><h4 id="Bi数"><a href="#Bi数" class="headerlink" title="==Bi数=="></a>==Bi数==</h4><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209191722825.png" alt="QQ截图20220919164104"></p><h2 id="4-2-零维问题的集总参数法"><a href="#4-2-零维问题的集总参数法" class="headerlink" title="4.2 零维问题的集总参数法"></a>4.2 零维问题的集总参数法</h2><p>（Bi&lt;=0.1）</p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209191722597.png" alt="QQ截图20220919172134"></p><h3 id="4-2-1-集总参数法温度场分析解"><a href="#4-2-1-集总参数法温度场分析解" class="headerlink" title="4.2.1 集总参数法温度场分析解"></a>4.2.1 集总参数法温度场分析解</h3><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209191745106.png" alt="QQ截图20220919172550"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209191745729.png" alt="QQ截图20220919172954"><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209191745926.png" alt="QQ截图20220919172656"></p><h3 id="4-2-2-导热量计算式、时间常数与傅里叶数"><a href="#4-2-2-导热量计算式、时间常数与傅里叶数" class="headerlink" title="4.2.2 导热量计算式、时间常数与傅里叶数"></a>4.2.2 导热量计算式、时间常数与傅里叶数</h3><h4 id="1-导热量计算式"><a href="#1-导热量计算式" class="headerlink" title="1. 导热量计算式"></a>1. 导热量计算式</h4><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209191744076.png" alt="QQ截图20220919173129"></p><h4 id="2-时间常数"><a href="#2-时间常数" class="headerlink" title="2. 时间常数"></a>2. 时间常数</h4><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209191744300.png" alt="QQ截图20220919173756"></p><p>==式(3)和时间常数==</p><h4 id="3-傅里叶数"><a href="#3-傅里叶数" class="headerlink" title="3. 傅里叶数"></a>3. 傅里叶数</h4><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209211614050.png" alt="QQ截图20220921161423"></p><p>==第一行公式、傅里叶数表达式==</p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209211707253.png" alt="QQ截图20220921161858"></p><h3 id="是否可以使用集总参数法的判断依据"><a href="#是否可以使用集总参数法的判断依据" class="headerlink" title="是否可以使用集总参数法的判断依据"></a>是否可以使用集总参数法的判断依据</h3><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209211707859.png" alt="QQ截图20220921162446"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209211707474.png" alt="QQ截图20220921162719"></p><h2 id="例题-5"><a href="#例题-5" class="headerlink" title="例题"></a>例题</h2><p>例4.1</p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209211707186.png" alt="QQ截图20220921164620"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209211707676.png" alt="QQ截图20220921164037"></p><p>例4.2</p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209211707326.png" alt="QQ截图20220921164420"></p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209211739317.png" alt="QQ截图20220921170533"></p><p>例4.3</p><p><img src="https://kunzhiyi.oss-cn-nanjing.aliyuncs.com/202209211739091.png" alt="QQ截图20220921171039"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
